SPECIAL SESSIONS:

* A Special Session Honoring John Reynolds on his 75th birthday, =
organised by Stephen Brookes (CMU) and Peter O=92Hearn (QMW, London).

* A Special Session on Systems Biology, held in conjunction J=E9r=F4me =
Feret=92s plenary talk, and organised by Jean Krivine (Paris VII & =
CNRS).

* A Special Session on Security, held in conjunction with Steve =
Zdancewic=92s plenary talk, and organised by Catherine Meadows (NRL).

TUTORIALS: There will be four tutorials on Programs from Proofs that =
will be given during the course of the meeting. The lectures are =
organised by Martin Escard=F3 and Achim Jung (Birmingham). The speakers =
include Ulrich Berger (Swansea), Martin Escard=F3 (Birmingham), Paulo =
Oliva (Queen Mary), and Monika Seisenberger (Swansea).

