IMPORTANT DATES:

- 21 February 2011      Title and Short Abstract submission deadline
- 28 February 2011      Paper submission deadline
- 31 March 31 2011      Notification to authors
- 15 April 15 2011      Preliminary proceedings version due

SUBMISSIONS should be prepared using ENTCS Macros, available from =
http://www.entcs.org. Submissions should be in the form of a PDF file =
not exceeding 15 pages in length. Submissions are now open on the =
EasyChair website:

http://www.easychair.org/conferences/?conf=3Dmfps2011

PROCEEDINGS: There will be a preliminary proceedings of the conference =
papers that will be distributed at the meeting, with a final proceedings =
published in ENTCS after the meeting.

The Organisers of the MFPS series are Stephen Brookes (CMU), Achim Jung =
(Birmingham), Catherine Meadows (NRL), Michael Mislove (Tulane) and =
Prakash Panangaden (McGill). The local arrangements for MFPS XXVII are =
being overseen by Stephen Brookes (CMU).

